Titolo: Jaseiken Necromancer

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Jaseiken Necromancer (邪聖剣 (じゃせいけん)ネクロマンサー) is a fantasy role-playing video game developed by Hudson Soft for the PC Engine. The original PC Engine version was only released in Japan.The game has never been officially translated into English despite becoming available as a downloadable purchase in United States and Europe.
A sequel, Necromancer 2, was released on mobile devices in Japan. It was ported to the DSi in 2010 and released as Jaseiken Necromancer: Nightmare Reborn.